title: The Fugitive S02E26 Masquerade DivX
description:
The Fugitive
S02E26
Masquerade

Airdate: March 23, 1965

    * One of 15 episodes from Season Two which have not been released on DVD
    * Remastered audio and video from VHS TV rip
    * Original music, not a synthesized replacement track

Mistaken identities may cost Kimble (David Janssen) his freedom. He's nabbed by the police---who think he's an important Government witness.

Mavis: Norma Crane. Hull: John Milford. Sheriff: Ed Asner.
